            "summary": "The way a mother holds her baby affects how easy it is for her baby to feed effectively. This video shows basic points important for any position and then demonstrates several common positions that have worked well for many mothers and babies.This video is intended primarily for mothers in the developing world, but may be helpful to breastfeeding mothers worldwide.",
