            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-10T06:24:14+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 02/10/2026 - 06:24\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Dai ndaigona Kukuudza . . . . \"Ndiwe, mubereki wangu anodiwa. Ndaiziva kuti uri pano, asi ikozvino ndiri kukuona zvakanaka. Ndinokunyemwerera uye ndinoda kuona zviso zvako zvichinyemwerera kwandiri. Ndaigona kukudzidza iwe kwenguva yakareba. Ndinoda kuteerera inzwi rako, uye ndinoda kubata kwako. Ndinosimudzirwa nekunyemwerera kwako, inzwi, uye kufamba kwako. Nenzira imwecheteyo, kunyemwerera kwangu, inzwi rangu uye kufamba zvinokurudzira kana zvichindiita kuti ndifambise ruoko rwangu, kunyanya kana uchitaridza chimwe chinhu. Ini ndinochida. nokuda kwayo. Ndiwo madzidzisiro andinoita zvino—ndinotarisa zvinhu, ndinoedza kuzviisa mumuromo mangu;",
