            "body": "\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUkuxhumana\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EYini Okutsha?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKusukela ekuzalweni komnyaka wesithathu kuze kufike umnyaka wesine, yisikhathi esiqakathekileyo kakhulu ekukhuleni kwenkulumo yomntanakho. Uzafunda amazwi amanengi amatsha ngokukulalela wena labanye abantu abadala, njalo ngokulalela izinganekwane. Kule minyaka, uba lentshisekelo enkulu kuzo zonke izinhlobo zokuxhumana. Uyakulangazelela ukukuxoxela izindaba loba ukuchaza izinto ezenzekayo. Ungabona ukuthi uyakujabulela kangakanani ukukhuluma lawe. Ngalesi sikhathi, uzazwisisa inengi lezinto ozitshoyo kuye, njalo angakwazi ukuqagela incazelo yamanye amazwi amatsha. Uzabona futhi ukuthi ekupheleni kwalomnyaka, imisho yomntanakho izabe seyinde kakhulu. Uzakwazi futhi ukulandela imilayo elobunzima obengeziwe enezingxenye ezimbili loba ezintathu, njengokuthi, “Ngicela uvale umnyango bese usiza kimi.”\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUngenzani Ukumncedisa?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENjengokuvamileyo, lalela umntanakho njalo ube lezingxoxo ezimnandi laye ngezikhathi zonke zosuku. Uzathola ukuthi kule minyaka, ulokunengi afuna ukukhuluma ngakho! Mfake kulokho okwenzayo njalo usebenzise lesosikhathi ukumupha imilayo ngendlela yokudlala loba ukumethulela amazwi amatsha athokozisayo engxoxweni. Bala njalo umxoxele izinganekwane nsuku zonke. Ungambuza ngendaba ukuthi ucabanga ukuthi kuzokwenzakalani ngokulandelayo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EImizwa\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EYini Okutsha?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIsikhathi esiphakathi komnyaka wesithathu lowesine siqakathekile kakhulu ekukhuleni kwemizwa yomntanakho. Ngalesi sikhathi, ufunda ukubona lokuqamba imizwa ehlukeneyo. Kule minyaka, angakwazi ukubona imizwa eyisisekelo enjengentokozo, usizi, ukwesaba lolaka. Ungambona eveza eminye imizwa njengokwesaba izinto ezingekhona sibili, ukukhathazeka ngendlela abanye abaziphatha ngayo, loba uthando lokunamathela kubantu azizwa eseduze labo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENxa enikwa ithuba, uzambona esenza abangane bakhe bokuqala kulomnyaka. Manje usezaqala ukudlala labanye ngokubambisana, emaqenjini amancane. Ukwabelana sekulula kancane, lanxa kungelula ngaso sonke isikhathi ngoba useqalisa ukuqonda ukuthi “ngokwami” lokuthi “ngokwake.”\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUngenzani Ukumncedisa?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EQhubeka usungula indawo ephephileyo lomntanakho. Lokhu kwenza kube lula kuye ukuveza lokulawula imizwa yakhe. Njengasesemncane, imikhuba yansuku zonke eqondakalayo iyamnceda azizwe ephephile. Mncede azi ukuthi kuzokwenzakalani ngokulandelayo lokuthi usuku lujwayele ukuba njani. Nxa ezizwa ephephile, uzakwazi ukuziphatha kahle.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENjengoba lobu bungane bokuqala buqakathekile kuye, zama ukudala amathuba okudlala labanye abantwana. Kodwa hlala useduze labo ngoba amakhono akhe okuxhumana labanye asakhula, njalo kungavela ukungezwani loba izingxabano. Uzamnceda ngokuphendula ngendlela ezolileyo leqondileyo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUkucabanga\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EYini Okutsha?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUkudlala kuseyindlela enkulu umntwana wale minyaka afunda ngayo futhi ahlole ngayo yena lomhlaba omuzungezileyo, kodwa manje “ukufunda ngokudlala” sekugcwele umcabango omkhulu. Angenza umdlalo wokunatha itiye loba azibone engudokotela onakekela ingane egulayo. Abanye abantwana baba labangane abacabangelwayo kule minyaka. Lanxa ethanda ukuzibumbela izinto, uyakwazi ukuhlukanisa phakathi kweqiniso lokucabanga. Lesi futhi yisikhathi lapho ethakazelela kakhulu umhlaba omuzungezileyo. Imibuzo, imibuzo, imibuzo imnceda ukufunda—ngubani? kuyini? kungani? Kungenzeka abe lentshisekelo enkulu ngomzimba wakhe leyezabanye.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKulomnyaka uzafunda imiqondo ephathelene lokuphambanisa izinto njengokuthi kukhulu/kuncane, kunengi/kuncane, kanye lamanye amagama anjengokuthi “phezu,” “phakathi,” “phansi.” Inkumbulo yakhe iyakhula, okumenza afunde izingoma ezimfushane aze azihlabele kamuva. Uzaqala ukukhomba lokuqamba ezinye izinhlamvu lezinombolo. Ngesikhathi efika eminyakeni emine, kungenzeka abale izinto ezifika kwezine njalo ahlukanise izinto ngokombala wazo lobume bazo obufanayo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUngenzani Ukumncedisa?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYamukela imibuzo yakhe eminengi njengendlela yakhe ebalulekileyo yokufunda ngomhlaba. Zama ukuphendula ngendlela elula leqotho ngaphandle kokunika izincazelo ezinzima kakhulu. Nxa ungelwazi ulutho, tsho njalo. Mtshengise indlela zokuthola ulwazi—ngokwesibonelo, nxa ebuza ngezinyoni azibonayo, ungathola ibhuku loba ukhulume lomakhelwane owaziyo ngezinyoni. Hlala uzimisela ukufuna impendulo ndawonye emabhukwini loba kwezinye izindlela zolwazi.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUkuhamba Lokunyakaza\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EYini Okutsha?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPhakathi kweminyaka emithathu leyemine, umntanakho uba lomdlandla omkhulu emzimbeni. Ungabona ukuthi uthokoza kangakanani zonke izinhlobo zokunyakaza. Usephucukile ekugijimeni, ekukhuphukeni, ekweqeni, lokuma ngomlenze owodwa. Angabamba ibhola elibhawuzayo kuye izikhathi ezinengi. Nxa kulezitebhisi lapho ahlala khona, usephucukile ekukhuphukeni kwazo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENgokunjalo, useqala ukuzimela kakhulu. Uyadla yedwa, uyakwazi ukuzigqokisa kakhulu, usebenzisa indlu yangasese yedwa, njalo uyazigeza.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUngenzani Ukumncedisa?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMqaphele njalo umncede kwezinye izingxenye zokuzinakekela ezisanzima, njengokuxubha amazinyo. Mbhekisise nxa ekhuphuka, umnike inkululeko yokuzimela kodwa uqaphele ukuphepha kwakhe. Mpheni amathuba okuzama imisebenzi ehlukeneyo, ikakhulu edinga ukunyakaza okunengi, kanye laleyo ethuleyo njengokudweba lokubuka amabhuku. Mfundise imidlalo yendabuko yangaphandle; dansa laye njalo ulingise ukunyakaza kwakhe njengoba naye engalingisa okwakho. Sekela imisebenzi ayithandayo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUkuze uthole ezinye izindlela ezinengi zokusekela ukukhula komntwana ngokudlala, yiya esigabeni esithi \u003Cstrong\u003EUkudlala Ndawonye\u003C/strong\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EUkukhathazeka Kwabazali Ngokukhula Phakathi Kwenyanga Yama-37 Kusiya Kuma-48\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENjengoba umntwana ngamunye ekhula ngendlela yakhe eyahlukileyo, akunakwenzeka ukubikezela ukuthi umntanakho uzaphumelela nini loba kanjani ekwenzeni ikhono elithile ngokupheleleyo. Amakhono alindelekileyo (izigaba zokukhula) alotshiweyo kulesi sikhathi akunika umqondo nje ojwayelekileyo wezinguquko ongazilindela njengoba ekhula. Ungakhathazeki nxa ukukhula kwakhe kulandela enye indlela encane ehlukileyo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKodwa-ke, khuluma lodokotela, unesi loba umhlinzeki wezempilo nxa umntanakho ekhombisa noma yiziphi izimpawu ezilandelayo zokubambezeleka ekukhuleni, nxa kubonakala sengathi ulahlekelwe ngamanye amakhono ayenawo ngaphambili, loba nxa ulezinye izizathu zokukhathazeka:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAkabonisi intshisekelo yokudlala labanye loba yokudlala imidlalo yokuzibumbela.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUyabanganaki abanye abantwana loba akaphenduli kubantu abangaphandle komndeni.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAkakwazi ukweqa esendaweni eyodwa.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUlobunzima ekudwebeleni (ukwenza imivimbo ephepheni).\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAkalandeli umyalo olengxenye ezintathu.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAkakwazi ukuxoxa indaba ayithandayo.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E",
